{
  "stem": "23350.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were only a family with this one child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he asked me that-- well, apparently, she wanted someone to look after the child, to go for a walk with them more than anything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother wouldn't allow it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother said no, none of my children are going to work for anybody and any Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And just leave us alone, and don't come to our house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I had the feeling that I wanted to do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's really like fate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I ran after him, and I said, I want to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I will go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that helped us so much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First of all, because when I went upstairs, and I came upstairs, and I was wearing a scarf.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I put a big scarf on, which my mother once made, like a crochet scarf, different colors it had.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had my stars of David, one front and one in the back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I came upstairs, and she said I should take the scarf off, and she saw that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She said, this you will not wear in my place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So straightaway, I had to take these off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I could go everywhere for a walk with the little girl.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I didn't wear the star.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I could do what I wanted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everybody who wanted something-- sometimes they had a headache or toothache, or this or that-- I was always running to the chemists, because I could go, you see.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And what's more, when I went past the where the magistrate is, because the chemist was behind there, and the burgermeister had his office.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And do you know, the window was always open summertime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Wide open.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would wave to him and say hello, he would wave right back.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
